    "chain_flexibility_notes": "Exists in two families with very different behavior: rigid/unplasticized PVC (uPVC) and flexible PVC (can be >85% plasticizer by mass).",
    "tg_relation_notes": "Rigid PVC's Tg (82°C) is well above room temperature, giving unplasticized PVC its stiffness; plasticizer addition lowers the effective Tg dramatically, producing flexible PVC."
